verbose_text: In comparison, AV appears to be a more passive PS binding protein : AV did not affect the clearance of the degenerating dendrites or cause degeneration of CDC50 KO neurons, but was often located in intracellular vesicles in PS exposing neurons, likely a result of endocytosis.
evidence: AV did not affect the clearance of the degenerating dendrites or cause degeneration of CDC50
